2025-09-11 02:52:11 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-11 02:52:11 [INFO] Can continue: That doesn't sound too safe. What if we damage the<br>ruins? Surely it's better to go slower and preserve as<br>much as we can?
