2025-09-11 03:09:44 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:09:44 [INFO] Can continue: Vanstrom Klause
2025-09-11 03:09:44 [INFO] Can continue: Hello there. The name's Vanstrom Klause. How goes it<br>stranger?
2025-09-11 03:09:44 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 03:09:45 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:09:45 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-11 03:09:45 [INFO] Can continue: Quite well, thanks for asking. How about you?
2025-09-11 03:09:45 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 03:09:46 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:09:46 [INFO] Can continue: Vanstrom Klause
2025-09-11 03:09:46 [INFO] Can continue: Hmm, well, I am a little concerned about some friends<br>of mine. They're in dire need of some assistance, but<br>I'm at a loss as to how I can help them.
2025-09-11 03:09:46 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 03:09:47 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:09:47 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-11 03:09:47 [INFO] Can continue: What friends are these?
2025-09-11 03:09:47 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 03:09:48 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:09:48 [INFO] Can continue: Vanstrom Klause
2025-09-11 03:09:48 [INFO] Can continue: It's a personal tragedy that I have yet to meet them in<br>the flesh. But their exploits make mouth watering<br>stories... The real meat and drink of high adventure<br>and daring... So they say.
2025-09-11 03:09:48 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 03:09:48 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:09:48 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-11 03:09:48 [INFO] Can continue: What does that mean exactly? I mean, I have some<br>stories. I'm quite a hero myself, you may actually be<br>talking about me?
2025-09-11 03:09:48 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 03:09:49 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:09:49 [INFO] Can continue: Vanstrom Klause
2025-09-11 03:09:49 [INFO] Can continue: They're a group of rebels fighting against the vampyres<br>that rule over Morytania. They're known as the<br>Myreque. Some people call them terrorists while others<br>call them freedom fighters!
2025-09-11 03:09:49 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 03:09:49 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:09:49 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-11 03:09:49 [INFO] Can continue: I see. And you want to help them?
2025-09-11 03:09:49 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 03:09:50 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:09:50 [INFO] Can continue: Vanstrom Klause
2025-09-11 03:09:50 [INFO] Can continue: Of course. I'm a big fan of their cause. I was hoping to<br>supply them with some new weapons. Alas, I find that<br>I'm rather lacking in ability when it comes to this kind<br>of thing!
2025-09-11 03:09:50 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 03:09:51 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:09:51 [INFO] ===
2025-09-11 03:09:51 [INFO] Yes.
2025-09-11 03:09:51 [INFO] No.
2025-09-11 03:09:51 [INFO] ===
2025-09-11 03:09:51 [INFO] 1167 Option: 1 Yes.
2025-09-11 03:09:52 [INFO] ANTIBAN: mouse_off_screen
2025-09-11 03:09:54 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:09:54 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-11 03:09:54 [INFO] Can continue: Well perhaps I could take these weapons to the<br>Myreque. What do they need?
2025-09-11 03:09:54 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 03:09:55 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:09:55 [INFO] Can continue: Vanstrom Klause
2025-09-11 03:09:55 [INFO] Can continue: Really? You would help?
2025-09-11 03:09:55 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 03:09:55 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:09:55 [INFO] Can continue: Vanstrom Klause
2025-09-11 03:09:55 [INFO] Can continue: I was hoping to deliver some steel to them. A longsword,<br>two shortswords, a dagger, a mace and a warhammer.
2025-09-11 03:09:55 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 03:09:56 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:09:56 [INFO] Can continue: Vanstrom Klause
2025-09-11 03:09:56 [INFO] Can continue: Though if you wish to do this, I'm afraid you'll need to<br>aquire the weapons yourself. My efforts to procure<br>them have been rather unsuccessful.
2025-09-11 03:09:56 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 03:09:57 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:09:57 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-11 03:09:57 [INFO] Can continue: Right. Get some steel weapons and take them to the<br>Myreque. Where can I find them?
2025-09-11 03:09:57 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 03:09:58 [INFO] Solving dialogue
