2025-09-11 03:11:12 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:11:12 [INFO] Can continue: Cyreg Paddlehorn
2025-09-11 03:11:12 [INFO] Can continue: Don't dare to judge me young fool... what do you<br>know of the heartache I carry? I want to help them! I<br>did help them! But my part is done now. To do any<br>more is to risk death!
