2025-09-11 03:11:13 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:11:13 [INFO] Can continue: Cyreg Paddlehorn
2025-09-11 03:11:13 [INFO] Can continue: Hmmm. Very well, if you would take your chance to<br>help these strangers, who am I to stop you?
