2025-09-11 03:11:15 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:11:15 [INFO] Can continue: Cyreg Paddlehorn
2025-09-11 03:11:15 [INFO] Can continue: You'll be going through Mort Myre though, so I won't<br>be letting you go unless you've got some defence<br>against the ghasts.
