2025-09-11 03:15:24 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:15:24 [INFO] Can continue: Veliaf Hurtz
2025-09-11 03:15:24 [INFO] Can continue: I don't understand though. He said you led him here.<br>How?
2025-09-11 03:15:24 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 03:15:24 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:15:24 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-11 03:15:24 [INFO] Can continue: He was the one that asked me to bring the weapons to<br>you. He looked like a human though.
2025-09-11 03:15:24 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 03:15:26 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:15:26 [INFO] Can continue: Veliaf Hurtz
2025-09-11 03:15:26 [INFO] Can continue: I'm sorry friend, but he clearly took advantage of you.<br>Vampyres can shapeshift to look like humans. Someone<br>from around here might have realised. You were not to<br>know though.
2025-09-11 03:15:26 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 03:15:26 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:15:26 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-11 03:15:26 [INFO] Can continue: No. I'm still responsible though.
2025-09-11 03:15:26 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 03:15:27 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:15:27 [INFO] Can continue: Veliaf Hurtz
2025-09-11 03:15:27 [INFO] Can continue: The burden of what happened here is for your<br>conscience to bear. That said, you managed to kill that<br>pet of his. We might all be dead if not for you.
2025-09-11 03:15:27 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 03:15:29 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:15:29 [INFO] Can continue: Veliaf Hurtz
2025-09-11 03:15:29 [INFO] Can continue: I imagine you now see why we fight for our freedom.
2025-09-11 03:15:29 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 03:15:31 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:15:31 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-11 03:15:31 [INFO] Can continue: Yes. I think I understand. Is there anything I can do<br>to help now? I first met Vanstrom in Canifis. I could<br>go back and see if he's still there?
2025-09-11 03:15:31 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 03:15:32 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:15:32 [INFO] Can continue: Veliaf Hurtz
2025-09-11 03:15:32 [INFO] Can continue: I suspect he will have moved on now. You're welcome<br>to try though. I know a shortcut that you might find<br>useful.
2025-09-11 03:15:32 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 03:15:32 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:15:32 [INFO] Can continue: Veliaf Hurtz
2025-09-11 03:15:32 [INFO] Can continue: If you head back into the main cave and go north<br>you'll reach a wall. There's a hidden door in that wall<br>that leads right into the basement of the Hair of the<br>Dog Tavern.
2025-09-11 03:15:32 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 03:15:33 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:15:33 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-11 03:15:33 [INFO] Can continue: That's very useful. Thanks.
2025-09-11 03:15:33 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 03:15:33 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 03:15:33 [INFO] Can continue: Veliaf Hurtz
2025-09-11 03:15:33 [INFO] Can continue: Once you are done, I'd appreciate you coming back<br>here to discuss a few things. You held your own<br>against that creature. We could use someone like you.
